.SS "void sgAddFilePath (const char * dir)"
.PP
Add a search path to the list. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIdir\fP The path to add (preferrably without trailing slash)
.RE
.PP

.SS "FILE * sgOpenFileFp (const char * name, const char * mode)"
.PP
Opens a file and returns a stdio file pointer. 
.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIname\fP Filename 
.br
\fImode\fP mode as passed to fopen()
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
valid FILE * on success or NULL on error
.RE
.PP

